cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.MM

The paper deals with the application of deep learning to classify microscopic images of various fungi species. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The use of machine learning and bag-of-words also suggests that the paper could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), or cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Finally, the mention of reducing the cost of diagnostic examination suggests that the paper could also belong to cs.MM (Multimedia).
